name: Friko
description:
Fetish hanger "Friko" consists of a used bicycle handle bar, stem and saddle mounted on a 21mm (0,8 in.) oval wood plate. "Friko" is fitted with strong bails and can carry heavy load when mounted properly. 

....................................................

All "Fetish Hangers" consist of used bicycle parts. All parts have been thoroughly cleaned but carry signs of usage. This is fully intentional and part of the project. All hangers feature my personal badge and their corresponding name on the backside.
